# =============================================================
# The Reindeer — files that must NOT be deployed to the live site.
# Anything matched here stays local and is never pushed to GitHub /
# Netlify. The public site only needs the page folders, css/, js/,
# assets/, _data/, admin/, netlify.toml, index.html and the two root
# logos (reindeer-full.png, the-reindeer.svg).
# To force-add an ignored file later: git add -f <file>
# =============================================================

# --- OS junk ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# --- Editor / tooling ---
.claude/
.vscode/
.idea/

# --- Project working documents (would be publicly readable if deployed) ---
*.md
*.docx
*.doc
*.txt
!robots.txt
*.csv
*.zip

# --- Docx / discovery extraction artifacts ---
pd_extracted/
unpacked_decisions/
unpacked_discovery/
Approved/

# --- Reference / experiment HTML (not part of the site) ---
The Harwood Arms.html
The Harwood Arms_files/
curtain.html
curtain-demo.html
modusmedia-dark.html
modusmedia-light.html

# --- Working screenshots and loose images NOT referenced by the site ---
Screenshot *.png
